持香港人 爭取民主？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T02:55:31.000Z","msg":"個學者唔明大陸個種腐敗。根本大陸唔係有咁多美資外資，其實同菲律賓國家一撚樣質素"},{"pid":"0fc3f8051f91efb828cfcf711f286ca2b1dee48c","tid":2228822,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T02:57:50.000Z","msg":"就算有10億支那人支持香港都冇用，佢地都冇權"},{"pid":"691f7567e3328b12a46ec73fcf1c8f9b171909c2","tid":2228822,"uid":239345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7a061c7bcb708e3633e70d7ac2e805f624a4161b","tid":2228822,"uid":39049,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"100f6432128b098e104910c803c31f89a1aab997","tid":2228822,"uid":42188,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T02:40:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span class=\"red\">只是西方國家要時間適應，理解到「一國兩制」並沒有變化。</span></blockquote>點解西方國家要俾時間你？<br />\n又唔見女神俾時間去了解毒撚？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T02:43:23.000Z","msg":"就係越理解先越知咩事..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T03:04:10.000Z","msg":"毒撚：「全部都係雞！連你阿媽都係！」"},{"pid":"0b7ae3a7c53c7548f530723ff2bde3988ff9ab72","tid":2228822,"uid":254450,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7a061c7bcb708e3633e70d7ac2e805f624a4161b","tid":2228822,"uid":39049,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"100f6432128b098e104910c803c31f89a1aab997","tid":2228822,"uid":42188,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T02:40:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span class=\"red\">只是西方國家要時間適應，理解到「一國兩制」並沒有變化。</span></blockquote>點解西方國家要俾時間你？<br />\n又唔見女神俾時間去了解毒撚？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T02:43:23.000Z","msg":"就係越理解先越知咩事..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T03:05:17.000Z","msg":"依家個情況似係個女神已經觀察咗好耐，知條毒撚又樣衰性格又毒仲成身縮味。但係毒撚同佢講其實我好幽默，你未了解清楚我啫，不如我哋交換電話再了解吓大家啦一樣，柒撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"044c8a74a8cf96078cad52595579a3329ffc9d0a","tid":2228822,"uid":51121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT